Author: shiawase6946
Content:
It is also easier to manipulate the vote when many are golputs. Like this:

Pemilu use absensi as their way to count how many votes are there. When many are absent, many surat suara are empty. Tampering empty surat suara is easier than already used surat suara. Just write anybody name who is absent on absensi , grab one paper coblos anywhere you want. Put it back in the box. 

Where they could do this? Could be kecamatan, could be kota, could be provinsi.
